<p>John and Dave discuss using the old Apple Pro Speakers on newer Macs (good luck!), Time Machine issues when moving disks between Macs, syncing tasks/todos from your Mac to your iPhone, Mac HD webcams, and multiple clipboards. Subscribe today &mdash; it&rsquo;s cheap, just $25 for 6 months &mdash; and enjoy!</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
